{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"How to make the perfect iPad stand out of LEGO&#8217;s","content":"<img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"My LEGO iPad stand\" src=\"http://distilleryimage3.instagram.com/773be45aba2511e18cf91231380fd29b_7.jpg\" alt=\"My LEGO iPad stand\" width=\"428\" height=\"428\" />\n<p>Today I finally got fed up with the <em>&#8220;Make my <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"iPad\" href=\"http://www.apple.com/ipad/\" rel=\"homepage\" target=\"_blank\">iPad</a> stand up&#8221;</em>Â dance. You know the one:</p>\n<p><em>Leeeaaan the iPad ever so carefully against a stack of books. Slides. Falls. No good.</em></p>\n<p><em>Ok, maybe if I put some rubber bands under so it won&#8217;t slip &#8230;</em></p>\n<p><em>Nope.</em></p>\n<p><em>Maybe if I wedge it juuuuust right between the notebook and the books &#8230;</em></p>\n<p>After two years of dancing this dance &#8211; and being too cheap to buy a proper stand &#8211; I finally realized some of my <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Lego\" href=\"http://www.lego.com/\" rel=\"homepage\" target=\"_blank\">LEGO</a>&#8216;s possess the perfect angles to prop it up just right.</p>\n<h2>The LEGO iPad stand</h2>\n<p>After ~40 minutes of tinkering I had a stand. A simple, dare I say elegant?, stand. Only 30 pieces. Even the colours match so it&#8217;s definitely the most beautiful LEGO creation I have ever made!</p>\n<p>The angle did in fact turn out perfect. The whole thing is even sturdy enough to withstand wild tapping and swiping conditions. For bonus points, an iPhone also fits (I didn&#8217;t plan this one).</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s how you can make one yourself:</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_4677\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step0.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4677 \" title=\"Step 0: Get some LEGO's\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step0-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Step 0: Get some LEGO's\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step0-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step0-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step0.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Step 0: Get some LEGO&#39;s</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4678\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step1.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4678 \" title=\"Step1: put some spacers together\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step1-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Step1: put some spacers together\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step1-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step1-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step1.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Step1: put some spacers together</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4679\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step2.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4679 \" title=\"Step2: Spacers go in the big yellow bit\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step2-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Step2: Spacers go in the big yellow bit\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step2-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step2.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Step2: Spacers go in the big yellow bit</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4680\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step3.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4680 \" title=\"Step3: Start assembling the legs\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step3-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Step3: Start assembling the legs\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step3-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step3-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step3.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Step3: Start assembling the legs</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4681\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step4.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4681 \" title=\"Step4: this is where the iPad rests\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step4-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Step4: this is where the iPad rests\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step4-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step4-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step4.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Step4: this is where the iPad rests</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4682\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step5.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4682 \" title=\"Step5: finish assembling the main body\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step5-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Step5: finish assembling the main body\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step5-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step5-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step5.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Step5: finish assembling the main body</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4683\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step6.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4683 \" title=\"Step6: attach the main leg\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step6-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Step6: attach the main leg\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step6-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step6-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step6.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Step6: attach the main leg</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4684\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step7.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4684 \" title=\"Step7: two more placeholders\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step7-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Step7: two more placeholders\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step7-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step7-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step7.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Step7: two more placeholders</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4685\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step8.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4685 \" title=\"Step8: add the main weight supports\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step8-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Step8: add the main weight supports\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step8-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step8-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-step8.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Step8: add the main weight supports</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4686\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-done.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4686 \" title=\"Enjoy your new iPad stand\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-done-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Enjoy your new iPad stand\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-done-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-done-300x224.jpg 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/lego-ipad-stand-done.jpg 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Enjoy your new iPad stand</p></div>\n<h6 class=\"zemanta-related-title\" style=\"font-size: 1em;\">Related articles</h6>\n<ul class=\"zemanta-article-ul zemanta-article-ul-image\" style=\"margin-left: 0; display: inline-block; list-style-type: none;\">\n<li class=\"zemanta-article-ul-li-image zemanta-article-ul-li\" style=\"display: inline-block; vertica